&lt;p&gt;Applications are welcome for the post of Specialty Doctor for the Centralised Place of Safety at the Maudsley Hospital in London.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be working as an integral part of a MDT, comprising a full nursing team, unit manager and Consultant Psychiatrist. The post provides an excellent opportunity to gain experience of innovative multiagency working, to contribute to clinical governance in the unit, and teaching and development of the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post would also suit existing trainees wishing to take time out of training via an OOOP, which could enable the clinical experience to count towards CCT.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marta Dell&#39;Aringa - Associate Medical Director&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email Address Marta.DellAringa@slam.nhs.uk - Telephone number 07986049590&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prof Vivienne Curtis, email: Vivienne.Curtis@slam.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
